{"tid":2300724,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日靚宵夜","createTime":"2020-11-25T17:45:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T17:57:47.000Z","uid":251736,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7a39f0b28d854ce528113dd9ec6d09f60c5e8157","tid":2300724,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LtX7rOM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtX7rOM.jpg&h=3e96f834&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三文魚排，用鹽解凍，之後落照燒汁搽勻，上面再切小小紋，再加一pat照燒汁係面，160度上下火13分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n食後感：中間啱啱熟完全唔乾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，上面有照燒汁嘅位置明顯滑d，下次唔應該慳住d照燒汁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9CM8bgX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9CM8bgX.jpg&h=07cf3e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4粒溫泉蛋，要拎定出黎令d蛋變返室溫，煲水到底下有小小泡，水嘅分量一定要過到面，之後熄火放蛋，焗17分半鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有個烏東不過冇影"},{"pid":"431850b5b0751559148650cc41555923b3caded1","tid":2300724,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:46:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dfb6b141303ca60f3bef3e00357c0a5f0f80dff1","tid":2300724,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:46:29.000Z","msg":"好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad6f910bdd5f645a6c1cba7c7aaba541e2471fc","tid":2300724,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:46:43.000Z","msg":"肥死了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdfbd848460fe9da4e721a0afd519c78d04be33c","tid":2300724,"uid":251736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2dfe69cf00a69e5813b22e84a5d4c